{"word":"σιωπάω","slug":"σιωπάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>σιωπάω</el></b> [<el>σιωπή</el> ‘silence’] <b>observe silence<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> by refraining from making an utterance <b><a href='B:470 26:63'>Mt 26:63</a>; <a href='B:480 3:4'>Mk 3:4</a>; <a href='B:480 9:34'>9:34</a>; <a href='B:480 14:61'>14:61</a>; <a href='B:510 18:9'>Ac 18:9</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> by ceasing to speak <b><a href='B:470 20:31'>Mt 20:31</a>; <a href='B:480 10:48'>Mk 10:48</a>; <a href='B:490 18:39'>Lk 18:39</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:490 19:40'>19:40</a>.</b> Of one who loses the ability to speak <b><a href='B:490 1:20'>1:20</a>.</b> Of becoming quiet, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ impv.\">impv.</a> <el>σιώπα</el> shut up! <b><a href='B:480 4:39'>Mk 4:39</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Σιών\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:σιωπῇ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}